data.description: Nestled in a charming gated community just about 7 miles from the beach, this townhome is a harmonious blend of comfort and functionality. The heart of this home, the kitchen, is adorned with mocha cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless-steel appliances. The living room and dining area is bathed in natural light, featuring recessed lighting that sets a cozy ambiance, perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests. The spacious master suite is a sanctuary, offering a walk-in closet and dual sinks in the master bathroom. Full-sized front-loading washer and dryer, central A/C, and ceiling fans in the bedrooms ensure the comfortable lifestyle. 2-car garage provides the space for parking and storage, adding practical convenience to your daily living. Dive into the community pool, unwind in the hot tub, or take a leisurely stroll in the nearby park.  Walk to nearby stores, restaurants, schools, and parks. Experience the perfect blend of privacy, convenience, and community in this charming townhome. No Mello-Roos adds to the appeal, making this an exceptional opportunity. Schedule a viewing today and make this your new home sweet home!
